      • getHqlConstraint

        public String getHqlConstraint()
        Description copied from class: Credentials
        Get an HQL constraint that will be used to match this credential to one in the database based on the identifying characteristics of this credential. See PrincipalDAO.savePrincipal(Principal) for usage. The credential entity should be referenced using alias "cred" in the constraint.
        Specified by:
        getHqlConstraint in class Credentials
        Returns:
        an HQL constraint (never should be empty or null)

      • getSSOId

        @NotEmpty
public String getSSOId()
        Get ssoId. This is the unique identifer that comes from the SSO Authority. It should never change. The format will vary by sso scheme.
        Returns:
        the ssoId
